		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Is it linear and headerless (.bin or .gen) or interleaved and with a copier header (.smd)? If headerless, you can just go to Command Prompt and<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">copy /b file.gen+file.gen bigger.gen</div>

		

		</td>
